I"<h1 id="cohesive-colors">Cohesive colors</h1>
<p>In order to achieve a well-balanced color scheme, Erica Schoonmaker introduced <a href="https://dribbble.com/shots/166246-My-Secret-for-Color-Schemes">Cohesive Colors</a> in a 2016 Dribbble shot. To ensure that a color scheme doesn’t consist of both harsh and soft tones, which usually doesn’t work outside of <a href="https://brutalistwebsites.com">brutalist design</a>, she overlays a central color on the others with reduced opacity, and chooses the colors that result from it.</p>
